section(class="template-wrapper act_1"  ng-init="s_actividad = 1")
    aside(class="template-asideLeft o-aside-Item")
        button(class="c-btn-IconAction" data-activities-count="1" ng-click="s_actividad = 1" ng-class="(s_actividad == 1) ? 'is-active' : '';")
        button(class="c-btn-IconAction" data-activities-count="2" ng-click="s_actividad = 2" ng-class="(s_actividad == 2) ? 'is-active' : '';")

    |
    |
    div(class="template-section m-a")
        section(class="template-content u-animationFadeDown" ng-show="s_actividad == 1")

            div(class="row row-flex")
                h5  Read the following excerpt and choose the correct answers.
            .row.ta-c
                img(src="unit_1/module_1/assets/images/self_2_1.png", alt="", class="u-responsive-img")

        section(class="template-content " ng-show="s_actividad == 2")

            h5 Choose the correct answers.
            .row-flex.align-items-center.mt20
                div(class="col xs12 md4 ta-c mb30")
                    img(src="unit_1/module_1/assets/images/self_2_2.png", alt="", class="u-responsive-img")

                div(class="col xs12 md8")
                    div(class="row row-flex")

                        div(class="row col-center")
                            p #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] This text discusses...
                                .row
                                    input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_1" id="selInput_1" value="1")
                                    label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_1")  The quality of MBAs in national and international universities.
                                    input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_1" id="selInput_2" value="2")
                                    label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_2") Gender inequity between men and women.
                                    input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_1" id="selInput_3" value="3")
                                    label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_3") The reasons why a candidate was not selected for a promotion.
                        div(class="row col-center")
                            p #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] The person who writes this complaint is a woman...
                                .row
                                    input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_2" id="selInput_4" value="1")
                                    label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_4") Who works as a receptionist
                                    input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_2" id="selInput_5" value="2")
                                    label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_5") With professional certifications.
                                    input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_2" id="selInput_6" value="3")
                                    label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_6") Who has no experience.
                        div(class="row col-center")
                            p #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] In order to make her argument stronger, the author...
                                .row
                                    input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_3" id="selInput_7" value="1")
                                    label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_7") Summarizes gender discriminations cases around the world.
                                    input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_3" id="selInput_8" value="2")
                                    label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_8") Talks only about her case.
                                    input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_3" id="selInput_9" value="3")
                                    label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_9") Mentions that if she doesn’t get the promotion, she will quit.
                        div(class="row col-center")
                            p #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] It can be inferred that this passage...
                                .row
                                    input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_4" id="selInput_10" value="1")
                                    label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_10") Is part of a letter of complaint.
                                    input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_4" id="selInput_11" value="2")
                                    label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_11") Appeared in a newspaper or magazine.
                                    input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_4" id="selInput_12" value="3")
                                    label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_12") Is criticizing the promotion system in a company.

